rows.label: tlk70000077_02_msg0001
rows.name:
What do you think about relations
between Iira and Gula?

rows.label: tlk70000077_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Iira's developing machine
technology, but their soil is bad,
so they can't get good crop yields.

rows.label: tlk70000077_02_msg0003
rows.name:
And Gula can farm plenty from
their huge swaths of fertile land, but
their technology is one step behind.

rows.label: tlk70000077_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I think we Superbians should try to
build friendly relationships with both
countries.

rows.label: tlk70000077_02_msg0005
rows.name:
If we could act as mediators between
those two, I think we could forge a
strong three-way alliance between us.

rows.label: tlk70000077_02_msg0006
rows.name:
But when it comes to cooking, I guess
there'll be some hurdles that are
impossible to overcome. Hahaha!
